{"tid":1510242,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"見到十幾歲嘅前線，可否自發睇住佢哋？","createTime":"2019-08-27T06:12:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T02:26:45.000Z","uid":80036,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"551733231589fba09530d80a205c6aa8bd206379","tid":1510242,"uid":80036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T06:12:27.000Z","msg":"社會要逼到咁年輕嘅手足上街，我哋當然冇辦法阻止佢哋出尼。<br />\n<br />\n做大人嘅可唔可以幫下手，唔好話照顧住佢地，起碼留意下佢哋嘅去向。<br />\n<br />\n俾狗追嗰陣唔該帶埋佢哋走，<br />\n走到嘅起碼知道佢哋後面冇狗，安全先好離開!<br />\n<br />\n依啲唔係叫照顧，係最基本嘅 team work 。<br />\n<br />\n咁簡單，所有人都做到!"},{"pid":"94101633c9604819f707f928e1e14b37c5a7178a","tid":1510242,"uid":33930,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T06:13:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PWzcvgg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPWzcvgg.jpg&h=187c67d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=9rGlslGXeLGLpJWMZA8biwUT8Qe%2F7ZKEe33%2FbaB1Hos%3D&h=45ed1049\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=9rGlslGXeLGLpJWMZA8biwUT8Qe%2F7ZKEe33%2FbaB1Hos%3D&h=2ced45e5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=9rGlslGXeLGLpJWMZA8biwUT8Qe%2F7ZKEe33%2FbaB1Hos%3D&h=dbeda820\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a>"},{"pid":"da7572e09f2cfdb0ba377fa46a56dc3e402864f9","tid":1510242,"uid":60310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T06:17:03.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"ec97d173f82090c7f6bf497bd64209d941ee7a2f","tid":1510242,"uid":86451,"like":1,"dislik